  "ModConfigMenu.IsQuickStackVisuallyOverrideFillStacksButton.Name": "Visually override Add To Stacks?",
  "ModConfigMenu.IsQuickStackVisuallyOverrideFillStacksButton.Desc": "(Requires \"Quick Stack with Add To Stacks?\" to be enabled.)\nIf enabled, the \"Add To Existing Stacks\" button in chest menus will be\nvisually overridden as a \"Quick Stack Items\" button.",

