  "ModConfigMenu.IsEnableQuickStackPrioritizeChest.Desc": "(Requires \"Toggle quick stack per-chest?\" to be enabled.)\nIf enabled, the Toggle Quick Stack button can also assign a priority level for that specific chest.\nChests with a higher priority level will be considered first when quick stacking.",

  "ModConfigMenu.IsQuickStackToggleChestButtonHidden.Name": "Hide Toggle Quick Stack button?",
  "ModConfigMenu.IsQuickStackToggleChestButtonHidden.Desc": "(Requires \"Toggle quick stack per-chest?\" to be enabled.)\nIf enabled, the Toggle Quick Stack button will be hidden from chest menus.\nEven when hidden, a chest's toggle/prioritize quick stack setting will still be used.",

